properties.name: trapsender.destination.ip
properties.description: Destionation IP address to which traps are sent

properties.name: trapsender.destination.port
properties.description: Destination port to which traps are sent

properties.name: trapsender.enterprise
properties.description: Enterprise ID to be sent in traps, if not set default snmp4j value will be used

properties.name: trapsender.authprotocol
properties.description: Authentication protocol for the user (NONE, MD5, SHA)

properties.name: trapsender.privprotocol
properties.description: Privacy protocol for the user (NONE, DES, AES)

properties.name: trapsender.source.ip
properties.description: Source IP address from which traps are sent
